Achievements.Name: Get On My Level
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on any difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Aren't You Thankful?
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on Hardcore Mode.

Achievements.Name: Epic Tier 4 Engineer
Achievements.Description: Complete the game in Classic Mode.

Achievements.Name: Survivalist
Achievements.Description: Complete the game in Pure Survival Mode.

Achievements.Name: My Buddy
Achievements.Description: Retrieve Resources from a Scavenger Bot at a Bench.

Achievements.Name: Metal Detector
Achievements.Description: Successfully deploy Scavenger Bots to 15 Resource Areas.

Achievements.Name: Circuit's Edge
Achievements.Description: Add a Circuit to a Weapon.

Achievements.Name: Full House
Achievements.Description: Craft a Weapon with 2 Tools, Tips, and Attachments with all Circuit slots filled.

Achievements.Name: Master Plan
Achievements.Description: Create a Blueprint that needs at least 2000 resources worth of parts and Circuits to build.

Achievements.Name: From the Jaws
Achievements.Description: Save your Co-Op partner from an execution by killing the attacker.

Achievements.Name: Share and Share Alike
Achievements.Description: Use the RIG to give an item to your Co-Op partner.

Achievements.Name: Ghosts of the Past
Achievements.Description: Face all of Carvers demons by completing all Co-Op only optional missions.

Achievements.Name: Architect
Achievements.Description: Share a Blueprint with your Co-Op partner.

Achievements.Name: Payback
Achievements.Description: Kill a Soldier by TK'ing a grenade or rocket back at them.

Achievements.Name: Slow Mo
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 enemies while they are in stasis.

Achievements.Name: Empty Chamber
Achievements.Description: Kill 30 enemies using melee strikes or a melee Weapon Part.

Achievements.Name: Electric Lawnmower
Achievements.Description: Kill 30 enemies using an electrified Ripper blade.

Achievements.Name: Overpowered Healing
Achievements.Description: Use quick heal to heal yourself 20 times.

Achievements.Name: Under a Buck
Achievements.Description: Shoot the deer head trophy in the Admiral's Quarters.

Achievements.Name: Space Ace
Achievements.Description: Shoot at least 70 targets during the ride to Tau Volantis.

Achievements.Name: Hungry
Achievements.Description: Reach the pump room of the Waystation without alerting any Feeders.

Achievements.Name: Drill Sergeant
Achievements.Description: Complete the Drill Room without taking any damage.

Achievements.Name: Weedkiller
Achievements.Description: Kill 5 Cysts in the Biology Building with a single poison gas cloud.
